ducing an error, creating small test cases for Coq bugs.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/JasonGross/coq-tools/blob/master/absolutize-imports.py\"><code>absolutize-imports.py</code></a> - Processes source files to make loading of dependencies robust against shadowing of file names.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/JasonGross/coq-tools/blob/master/inline-imports.py\"><code>inline-imports.py</code></a> - Creates stand-alone source files from developments by inlining the loading of all dependencies.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/JasonGross/coq-tools/blob/master/minimize-requires.py\"><code>minimize-requires.py</code></a> - Removes loading of unused dependencies.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/JasonGross/coq-tools/blob/master/move-requires.py\"><code>move-requires.py</code></a> - Moves all dependency loading statements to the top of source files.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/JasonGross/coq-tools/blob/master/move-vernaculars.py\"><code>move-vernaculars.py</code></a> - Lifts many vernacular commands and inner lemmas out of proof script blocks.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/JasonGross/coq-tools/blob/master/proof-using-helper.py\"><code>proof-using-helper.py</code></a> - Modifies source files to include proof annotations for faster parallel proving.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2021-08-25T18:02:51.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"tindzk/awesome-scala-native","categoryHTML":"<h2>Bindings</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/edadma/ncurses\">ncurses</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/edadma/ncurses\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #0